{
  "stem": "25639.8",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, this took him by surprise, and he said, I don't know anything about a secret-- about secret archives but if-- if there is, of course, we'll find out, and certainly we'll cooperate with you.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To make a long story short, nothing came of our meeting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have corresponded with Dr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Fulberg ?] Stuhlberg, and he wrote kind letters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "However, this factory was left unrecognized.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had another branch to the factory where they manufactured [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] other material and that-- Stocken-- and I think it was batteries for submarines, and a lot of people died.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A lot of the inmates died from lead poisoning in that factory and the factory could-- officials could see that there was no way out and that they have to recognize it, and so they, with the blessings-- well, the city put up the monument, and they cooperated in doing so, and I also went to that unveiling.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was very, very moving.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Stocken.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Also in Hannover.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's-- It's not Linden-Limmer, it's a different area called Stocken.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it is all over the world.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was in Mexico, I saw-- I saw them there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They are making rubber tires, the biggest in Europe in rubber tires, and they are making rubber accessories for refrigerators, washing machines, and other appliances, and they are still making gas masks.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went there, and I saw this man pull out a-- a gas mask, and it was still yellow, well it-- like chartreuse yellow, greenish yellow, and hot to the touch and was cooling and turning dark green in my hand.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I thought, times really have changed and modern machines.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I recall how we used to do it from thin sheet rubber and a form.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was totally different.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
